Belgium’s Leterme, Di Rupo Start Joint 2012 Budget Preparations

-- B y   J o h n   M a r t e n s
-- 
2011-09-15T10:48:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/belgium-s-leterme-di-rupo-start-joint-2012-budget-preparations.html
Belgium ’s caretaker Prime Minister
 Yves Leterme  and Elio Di Rupo, the leader of the French-speaking
Socialist Party who’s leading coalition talks, agreed to start a
joint working group to prepare the 2012 budget.  They will meet again on Sept. 23 to set an agenda for the
budget makeup, Di Rupo said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Martens at 
 jmartens1@bloomberg.net  